captions.name: IRA
captions.line: Right. It’s happening. I have got to move this shit around.

captions.name: HEXATE
captions.line: Ira? What are you doing Ira?

captions.name: IRA
captions.line: It’s got to go. This – look. Sick of it.
I just need it to be - not this anymore.

captions.name: HEXATE
captions.line: You seem a little agitated Ira.
Was it the banging of his fist on your door?
[snickering] What do you call a girl who hasn’t slept in days?
That sort of attention seeking won’t help
